menu "RoboTrickler"

    config ROBOTRICKLER_SCALE_TIMEOUT_MS
        int "Scale serial timeout (ms)"
        default 2000
        range 500 10000
        help
            How long to wait for a response from the scale before reporting
            a timeout. Increase if using a slow baud rate or long RS232 cable.

    config ROBOTRICKLER_DISP_STACK_SIZE
        int "LVGL display task stack size (bytes)"
        default 12288
        range 8192 32768
        help
            Stack size for the LVGL timer/render task (core 0).
            Increase if stack overflow is observed (check HWM in debug log).

    config ROBOTRICKLER_MAIN_STACK_SIZE
        int "Main loop task stack size (bytes)"
        default 12288
        range 8192 32768
        help
            Stack size for the main application loop task (core 1).
            Increase if stack overflow is observed (check HWM in debug log).

    config ROBOTRICKLER_HTTP_STACK_SIZE
        int "HTTP server task stack size (bytes)"
        default 12288
        range 8192 32768
        help
            Stack size for the ESP HTTP server task.
            Increase if stack overflow occurs during file upload/download.

endmenu
